      "value": "<p>You fire three small missiles from your mechanical form. Each missile hits a target of your choice that you can see within range. A missile deals 1d4+1 fire damage to its target. The missiles all strike simultaneously, and you can direct them to hit one target or several.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and create one additional missile.</p>",
